name: Carew Creek
description:
Introduction

In the Westland region on the South Island, if the water is too big to do Griffin Creek v4a5, then Carew is a great, fun, short romp with two beautiful 40m raps and a 5m rap, a 9m slide/jump, and a few other little jumps and slides.

Approach

Easy track tramping for 40 minutes.

Descent

Exit

Easy 15 minute creeking down to bridge where you park.
